Portugal Makes Request for Assistance From EU, Socrates Says

-- B y   J i m   S i l v e r
-- 
2011-04-06T19:44:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-06/portugal-is-seeking-financial-aid-from-eu-amid-debt-crisis-socrates-says.html
Portugal  has requested financial aid
from the European Union, Prime Minister  Jose Socrates  said.  “We’ve come to the moment in which not taking that
decision would bring risks the country can’t afford,” Socrates
said in a speech broadcast from the prime minister’s official
residence in Lisbon.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
